Morjana Alaoui (Arabic; a mụrụ na Nọvemba 30, 1982) bụ onye Moroccan-French na-eme ihe nkiri
Ọ pụtara na Marock, ihe nkiri egwu nke Pascal Laugier Martyrs, na Rock the Casbah

Alaoui biri ndụ ya n'oge ọ bụ nwata n'ógbè Anfa nke Casablanca, Morocco, ma gụọ akwụkwọ na Casablanca American School. Mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na asatọ, Alaoui kwagara Paris, France, ebe ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na Mahadum America nke Paris

Mgbe ọ na-aga mahadum, ọ zutere onye nduzi Laila Marrakchi, onye nyere ya ọrụ na ihe nkiri Marock (2005). A nabatara Marock nke ọma ma nye Alaoui aha mba. N'afọ 2007, ọ malitere ime ihe nkiri Martyrs, nke a makwaara ya maka ya. N'afọ 2016, Alaoui pụtara na ihe egwu na-akpali akpali nke Shaun Robert Smith duziri.
